{"title":"夕阳无限好——参观常州市青龙乡敬老院","authors":["刘章"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":3,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"夕阳无限好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——参观常州市青龙乡敬老院"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"院当中雪松似塔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西墙下一片菊花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已是深秋九月天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满院绿流香洒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六十多岁，八十上下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成一个新的家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声起，笑声起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"童音似春水哗哗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是生命的泉水呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灌溉得枯木也要发芽！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回忆自身清苦的童年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看每一棵野草都如诗似画……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甩几把扑克，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捻着一页页岁月；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说一说今昔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把生活的滋味品咂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟归巢夕阳斜挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人们院外溜达，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南水田里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映出美丽的晚霞。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}